♫   An air of melancholy surrounds me as the Bodhi leaves fall   ♫

14
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:27,600
   

15
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:30,300
   

16
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,900
We've already cleared the tracking incense. The heavenly soldiers won't come after us now.

17
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:40,200
I went ahead and sent a letter back to the mountain to ask for backup.

18
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,600
They'll detain her and take her back.

19
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:44,400
The most important thing now is to save Yan Dan.

20
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,600
Huan Qin must have set up a trap for us.

21
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:48,200
I've been playing against him for many years.

22
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:51,200
If I want to win, I have to calm myself first.

23
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,000
I can't make the first mistake.

24
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,800
You're right.

25
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,400
I know Yan Dan well.

26
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,400
She's smart and resourceful enough.

27
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,100
But the most important thing now...

28
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:01,500
Yu Mo.

29
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,000
Mountain Chief.

30
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:13,600
Bai Ling. Why are you so severely injured?

31
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,800
Did something happen to the mountain?

32
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,200
Yelan Mountain has been surrounded by 100,000 heavenly soldiers.

33
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,900
The barrier that you've put around the mountain is going to break soon.

34
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:23,600
Mountain Chief Zi Lin, the Fox Clan, and the Wolf Tribe are risking their lives to protect the mountain.

35
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:26,200
But there are too many heavenly soldiers.

36
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:29,000
Take Tao Ziqi back to the mountain first.

37
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:33,800
Huan Qin must be doing this because he wants to take those demons as hostages.

38
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:37,400
Yu Mo. You are the Mountain Chief.

39
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,600
Hurry, go back and help them.

40
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:42,100
But how I can leave Yan Dan behind?

41
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:49,100
Protecting the mountain is the same as protecting Yan Dan's home.

42
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:52,200
Leave it to me to rescue her.

43
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,200
I'll definitely bring her back.

44
00:02:58,100 --> 00:03:00,400
That's all we can do right now.

45
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:05,700
Ying Yuan. If you and Yan Dan are in danger, make sure to call me for help.

46
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:27,900
 I've searched all thirty halls in the north. 

47
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:31,100
 Yan Dan, where are you? 

48
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,600
 The Lotus qi? 

49
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,700
 Yuqing Palace. 

50
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:14,500
Yan Dan.

51
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:23,000
 This is a transfiguration spell. 

52
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:26,000
 But why is there Lotus qi here? 

53
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,400
I knew you would come.

54
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:33,900
Emperor Ying Yuan.

55
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:37,200
This Four-Leaf Lotus has weak immortal power.

56
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,600
She can't really be of use.

57
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:43,400
But I never thought that the fragrance of her real form could travel for miles.

58
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:46,000
It's quite calming for the mind.

59
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,700
Your enemy is me. You can just target me!

60
00:04:53,700 --> 00:04:55,300
We are evenly matched.

61
00:04:55,300 --> 00:05:00,400
If we have a fair fight, we may still be fighting after three days and three nights.

62
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:05,900
But now that I have Miss Yan Dan in my grasp, this changes things.

63
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:23,800
What do you want to do exactly?

64
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:29,600
What do you want to do exactly?!

65
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:56,500
 Ying Yuan. I'm sure you can see this. 

66
00:05:56,500 --> 00:06:00,100
 I know you'll definitely come to my rescue. 

67
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,700
Yan Dan!

68
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:52,600
Stop shouting. She can't hear you.

69
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,200
Her real form isn't here.

70
00:06:55,200 --> 00:07:02,000
Ying Yuan. When you played GO with Yan Dan back then, you hid the art of war within the GO manual.

71
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:09,000
Today, I've reset the pieces on the board and asked Miss Yan Dan to crack it for me again.

72
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:13,500
Unfortunately, she is so loyal to you.

73
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:15,800
She even refuses to help me with a small matter like this.

74
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:18,300
It's not the book of war that you want.

75
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,400
Tell me.

76
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:25,000
What exactly do I need to do for you to let her go?

77
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,400
Want to save her?

78
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:34,300
Give me your immortal spirit.

79
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:42,200
Huan Qin. You don't have to disguise yourself in front of me.

80
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:50,400
You've finally shown me your true self.

81
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:52,400
I know you.

82
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:57,300
Even if I give you my immortal spirit, you still won't let her go.

83
00:07:57,300 --> 00:08:02,100
And you'll butcher the Three Realms without any hesitation. Right?

84
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:08,900
Now, I've already absorbed all the immortal power of the Three Heavenly Emperors and the Heavenly Emperor.

85
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:11,200
I have millions of heavenly soldiers under my command.

86
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:16,300
If you insist on going to war with me, the Three Realms will turn to dust.

87
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:18,700
What's the point?

88
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:23,200
The most powerful beings in the Three Realms are just you and me.

89
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:25,800
We are both from the Asura Clan.

90
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:28,300
Why do you have to fight with me?

91
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:30,900
I've never wanted to fight you.

92
00:08:34,300 --> 00:08:36,000
In the past...

93
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:40,700
I sincerely treated you as my best friend.

94
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:45,200
But now... you are guilty of the most heinous crimes.

95
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,800
Even if I wasn't an Emperor,

96
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:52,000
I would still fulfill the duty of an Emperor.

97
00:08:55,300 --> 00:08:59,100
Ying Yuan. You've acted as Emperor Qingli for hundreds and thousands of years.

98
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:02,000
Have you ever been happy?

99
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:06,800
The Heavenly Emperor had only given you endless constraints and pressure.

100
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,500
But I'm different.

101
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:11,000
If you hand over your immortal spirit and stay out of it,

102
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:17,600
I swear that I will let you and Yan Dan live as a happy couple in the Mortal Realm.

103
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:20,600
I could never trust you anymore.

104
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:25,800
I will find her even if I have to travel through all Three Realms.

105
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:32,900
For the crimes you refuse to admit, there will be a day when I'll make you pay for them.

106
00:09:41,500 --> 00:09:47,100
Ying Yuan. I know that you won't abandon her.

107
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:49,200
I'll wait for you here.

108
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:07,500
 Ying Yuan. If you see me doing this, I hope you'll know what I'm thinking. 

109
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:32,300
There's something over there! Go after it!

110
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:37,200
 The Nine Heavens are heavily guarded. 

111
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,900
 Yan Dan isn't here. 

112
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:41,000
 I need to escape from here first. 

113
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:47,000
A lot has happened in the Heaven Realm. 
   

114
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:51,100
I know that everyone won't say anything on the surface, but all of you have frustrations about it.

115
00:10:51,100 --> 00:10:55,400
So, I've invited all of you to enjoy this lunar eclipse with me.

116
00:10:55,400 --> 00:11:00,300
Since we can't do anything right now, we can only drink our worries away.

117
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:03,200
Drink our worries away!

118
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:06,600
 Thank you for your kindness, Immortal Lady Yue Yao. 

119
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:11,700
Marshal. You're drunk again?

120
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:17,200
The situation is already what it is.

121
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:20,400
What else is there to hide?!

122
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:25,300
If the Heavenly Emperor wants to punish me for it, go ahead!

123
00:11:25,300 --> 00:11:28,000
I'd like to ask him some things!

124
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:31,550
He said that Emperor Ying Yuan colluded with

125
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:33,800
the Devil Realm to plot a rebellion with Tao Ziqi as the witness!

126
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:36,600
But you can fake a witness!

127
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:42,300
But you can't fake the Merfolk Tear and dragon scale that Emperor Ying Yuan had!

128
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:50,100
If he wasn't guilty, why didn't he take the dragon scale in his hand?!

129
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:56,400
He declared Emperor Ying Yuan guilty so hastily.

130
00:11:56,400 --> 00:12:01,000
How is that different from silencing someone with death?!

131
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:06,600
Marshal. The Heavenly Emperor has already issued the arrest warrant.

132
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:09,600
Ying Yuan is no longer an Emperor.

133
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:11,400
He's a wanted criminal among all the Three Re—

134
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:15,200
Emperor Ying Yuan was a hero of the War of Genesis!

135
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:18,200
He was the leader of the Four Emperors!

136
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,200
And the Heavenly Emperor ordered him to be killed just like that!

137
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:24,100
What about us?! When will it be our turn?!

138
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,600
I'm sorry for disturbing everyone.

139
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:36,200
Your Majesty!

140
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:43,400
Emperor Ying Yuan. Why are you here?

141
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,800
 Your Majesty. 

142
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:48,100
The Heavenly Emperor has kidnapped Yan Dan. I'm here to save her.

143
00:12:48,100 --> 00:12:49,800
He ambushed me.

144
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,600
He wants me to exchange my immortal spirit for her life.

145
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,800
Then, he framed me for assassinating him.

146
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:57,300
I never thought that I would run into all of you here.

147
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:01,300
 Sorry for disturbing your banquet! 

148
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:02,800
 We are here under the Heavenly Emperor's orders. 

149
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:04,400
 The traitor broke into the Heaven Realm tonight. 

150
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:06,400
 We've tracked him the whole way here. 
     

151
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:08,400
 I think we saw him entering your palace. 

152
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:10,600
 Can you allow us to search the place? 

153
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,800
The deities and I are enjoying the moon with some wine.

154
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:15,720
We haven't seen anyone suspicious entering my palace.

155
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,300
It's rare for Yueying Palace to have guests.

156
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:19,800
They are enjoying their night. How can I allow you to disturb them?

157
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,800
It's not that I don't trust you.

158
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:23,400
It's just a routine search.

159
00:13:23,400 --> 00:13:26,800
 If you are not happy about it, you can take it up to the Heavenly Emperor. 

160
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:32,400
You unruly brats!

161
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,600
The Heavenly Emperor has allowed you to behave so atrociously!

162
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:37,800
Now, you want to behave so rudely towards me?!

163
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:44,000
Don't you know that when I beat those deities in the Heaven Realm into pulp back then,

164
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:47,700
you weren't even born yet?!

165
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:50,000
I'm happily drunk right now!

166
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,700
I'm looking for something to do!

167
00:13:51,700 --> 00:13:54,600
If you dare take one step into Yueying Palace,

168
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:58,600
I'll take it that you want to fight me and go against me!

169
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:02,200
Get lost now!

170
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,400
We didn't know that you were here, Marshal. Sorry for offending you.

171
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:07,200
We'll search the other palaces first!

172
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:09,400
 Enjoy your night, Marshal! 

173
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,900
Let's go.

174
00:14:16,800 --> 00:14:19,600
Immortal Lady Yue Yao, let them in!

175
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:22,700
Don't stop me! Let me teach them how to fight!

176
00:14:22,700 --> 00:14:25,200
I'll knock their teeth out from their mouth!

177
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:28,100
You are indeed the Marshal. You are as imposing as ever.

178
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:30,500
Of course.

179
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:34,600
After you escaped from the Heavenly Gallows that day, the Heavenly Emperor was afraid

180
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:37,000
that there would be other high-level deities who held dissenting opinions like Zhi Xi

181
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,400
and who would turn against him eventually.

182
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:42,600
So, using the excuse of rebuilding the Heaven Realm, he removed us from our positions and duties.

183
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:45,200
That's why we all gathered here to share our sorrow.

184
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:51,500
If he has captured Miss Yan Dan, he won't imprison her in the Heaven Realm if he wanted to keep it a secret.

185
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:53,800
The Heavenly Prison is near Xuanxin Cliff.

186
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:57,900
After something happened to you, I've become even more alert.

187
00:14:57,900 --> 00:15:01,500
So, I use competitions as an excuse to go there often.

188
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:03,800
But there hasn't been any new prisoners.

189
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:07,600
But a few elite soldiers have been sent into the Mortal Realm.

190
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,800
But I don't know where they went.

191
00:15:09,800 --> 00:15:13,100
Marshal. I have a favor to ask.

192
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:14,400
And I can prove my innocence with it.

193
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:17,600
There's no need to be so courteous with me at a time like this!

194
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:20,400
What is it?

195
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:46,800
Immortal Lady Yue Yao. Marshal Huo De.

196
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:48,900
Is this how you enjoy the moon?

197
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:51,500
All of you are harboring the traitor, Ying Yuan.

198
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:54,400
Can I ask you what's the meaning of this?

199
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:56,800
Do you have any respect for the Heavenly Rules?!

200
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:59,500
What a joke! A traitor?

201
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:02,900
Can he be judged based on the testament of a mere celestial attendant?!

202
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:04,500
I...!

203
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:24,000
There's no need to frighten them.

204
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:27,200
I'm the one who threatened them to hide me here.

205
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:30,000
You should just target me.

206
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:33,200
The traitor, Ying Yuan, tried to take down the Heaven Realm.

207
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,000
He deserves to die!

208
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:39,400
Kill him and you'll be bestowed one thousand years of cultivation base and ascension to become a high-level deity!

209
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:46,300
Why aren't you doing anything? Attack him!

210
00:16:57,800 --> 00:17:00,600
There are millions of heavenly soldiers.

211
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:05,800
During the War of Genesis, the Divine-Devil War and the countless battles in the Devil Realm,

212
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:12,000
each and every one of the heavenly soldiers here were under Emperor Ying Yuan's command at some point.

213
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:15,500
All of them were once under his care.

214
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:22,400
Now you're asking them to turn their weapons against their former leader who was once their savior.

215
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:26,600
Do you think you can tempt them so easily with that?

216
00:17:26,600 --> 00:17:30,200
All of you had served under Emperor Ying Yuan for at least a few centuries.

217
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:32,400
Some have even served under him for thousands of years.

218
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:34,300
You all have gone through thick and thin together.

219
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:36,000
You know him very well.

220
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:38,900
There's no evidence showing that Emperor Ying Yuan betrayed the Heaven Realm.

221
00:17:38,900 --> 00:17:40,800
How can you convince yourself to turn against him?

222
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:42,400
How insolent of you!

223
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:46,000
Attack him!

224
00:17:55,100 --> 00:18:00,000
I won't kill you... because I don't want to become someone like you.

225
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:09,300
If you hurt my subordinates in front of me again, I will kill you.

226
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:27,100
I haven't visited the military camp for more than nine hundred years.

227
00:18:27,100 --> 00:18:29,000
   

228
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:31,800
Now, all of you have become great soldiers.

229
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:34,100
And you take good care of each other.

230
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:37,600
I'm proud of you.

231
00:18:37,600 --> 00:18:39,600
Back then, you put me on the horse to save me.

232
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:42,600
Today, let me escort you instead.

233
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:47,000
Emperor Qingli, Ying Yuan. Please take care of yourself.

234
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:49,400
We'll wait for your return!

235
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:06,000
He left just like that?

236
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:09,400
Those heavenly soldiers refused to attack him. They are useless.

237
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:11,000
I'm not talking about that.

238
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:14,300
Although Ying Yuan seems cold, he's incredibly loyal.

239
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:18,400
He wouldn't just abandon Yan Dan and leave her in danger!

240
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:21,600
Unless...

241
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:26,200
Arrange an army for me immediately. We are going to the Mortal Realm!

242
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,800
Yes, Your Majesty.

243
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:28,000
 The black piece should've taken the kill. 

244
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:30,700
 But Yan Dan jumped at Tian Yuan towards true north. 

245
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:33,800
 Among the Five Elements, true north means water. The black followed. 

246
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:35,500
 But Yan Dan chose to go forward. 

247
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:37,200
 In GO, it means calling out for help. 

248
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,400
 Then, she put another one below it. 

249
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:40,000
 The four pieces were lined up from top to bottom. 

250
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,400
 It was pointing to a direction. 

251
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:46,900
 Yan Dan is being kept in a waterfront that is two levels below the Heaven Realm. 

252
00:20:46,900 --> 00:20:48,900
 The only place that fits is the Night Forgetting River. 
    

253
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:51,000
 She must be here. 

254
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:12,360
Yan Dan!

255
00:21:19,700 --> 00:21:21,600
Ying Yuan!

256
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:23,260
You're all right now.

257
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:42,020
Are you okay?

258
00:21:42,620 --> 00:21:46,300
I'm fine. We're safe for now.

259
00:21:46,300 --> 00:21:51,020
I knew you would find me. I purposely made those three mistakes.

260
00:21:51,020 --> 00:21:55,580
I know. You're no longer the same Yan Dan as before.

261
00:22:37,180 --> 00:22:40,700
Why are you as foolish as His Majesty?

262
00:22:42,060 --> 00:22:45,270
With your bloodline, you could rule the Three Realms.

263
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:48,740
Why do you let yourself be distracted by love?

264
00:22:49,420 --> 00:22:52,960
He is Emperor Ying Yuan. Not the Young Lord of the Asura Clan.

265
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:55,320
Why are you doing this?

266
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:02,240
He can choose to abandon me and the Asura Clan,

267
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:10,740
but he'll always be my master.

268
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:18,700
Huan Qin, you traitor of the Asura Clan.

269
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:21,170
It won't end well for you!

270
00:23:21,170 --> 00:23:23,750
You are still spouting nonsense on your deathbed.

271
00:23:23,750 --> 00:23:25,940
I am the leader of the Three Realms.

272
00:23:25,940 --> 00:23:32,080
Today, both you and your master from the Asura Clan will die in my hands.

273
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,720
Master.

274
00:23:45,060 --> 00:23:46,900
Take care.

275
00:23:59,660 --> 00:24:01,920
I will remember...

276
00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:04,880
your sacrifice.

277
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:07,790
Ying Yuan, how dare you fool me.

278
00:24:07,790 --> 00:24:10,200
This is the price you'll have to pay.

279
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:14,200
There are many who can appreciate a winning game.

280
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:17,460
But no one appreciates a losing game.

281
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:23,000
Yan Dan. You were put in a losing game, but you managed to survive it.

282
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,770
I've learned from you.

283
00:24:24,770 --> 00:24:26,290
You are just not as good.

284
00:24:26,290 --> 00:24:28,600
You should have admitted defeat a long time ago.

285
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:36,980
Today, even if I have to destroy all of the Night Forgetting River, I will take Yan Dan away with me!

286
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:44,400
You know that if we fight, you won't be able to stop me.

287
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:48,720
I'm not trying to stop you.

288
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:51,200
But things can't always go your way.

289
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:58,640
If you take Yan Dan away today, those spirits in Yelan Mountain will be annihilated.

290
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:08,340
Yu Mo, your defense is like a bug trying to stop a cart!

291
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:10,700
Stop struggling. It's pointless.

292
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:13,740
We've already fully surrounded Yelan Mountain.

293
00:25:13,740 --> 00:25:20,340
Even if you can escape with the power of the Nine Fins... what about the lives of your fellow demons then?

294
00:25:20,340 --> 00:25:25,420
You want to threaten Yan Dan and Ying Yuan with Yelan Mountain.

295
00:25:25,420 --> 00:25:28,240
How naïve of you.

296
00:25:39,560 --> 00:25:41,780
We gathered heavenly fire.

297
00:25:41,780 --> 00:25:44,660
With an order from His Supreme Majesty,

298
00:25:44,660 --> 00:25:51,740
these demons and their beloved homeland will be burnt to a crisp.

299
00:25:54,360 --> 00:25:55,820
The Heavenly Rules are clear.

300
00:25:55,820 --> 00:25:57,360
You are forbidden to carry out a personal execution.

301
00:25:57,360 --> 00:26:00,620
You still need a clear reason just to deploy your army.

302
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:03,120
What did Yelan Mountain do wrong?!

303
00:26:03,120 --> 00:26:07,140
The demons in Yelan Mountain are working with Ying Yuan to plot a rebellion

304
00:26:07,140 --> 00:26:09,040
and disrespecting the Heaven Realm.

305
00:26:09,040 --> 00:26:10,960
They deserve to be punished with death.

306
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:13,860
You are the only one who accused Ying Yuan of that crime.

307
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:17,460
The Heaven Realm hasn't been convinced. Now you want to use that as an excuse to kill everyone.

308
00:26:17,460 --> 00:26:20,280
It will only make your fellow deities in the Heaven Realm despise you more.

309
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:23,480
Ying Yuan. My condition is still the same.

310
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:28,000
Hand over your immortal spirit and I will pardon the demons of Yelan Mountain.

311
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:31,900
You keep saying that you are going to fulfill your duty as the Emperor, right?

312
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:36,560
Now is the best chance for you to sacrifice yourself for the greater good.

313
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:39,280
Miss Yan Dan, you should try to convince him.

314
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:44,300
Is Ying Yuan's divine power more important than your friends' lives?

315
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:47,640
Ying Yuan, you mustn't!

316
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:55,680
Ying Yuan!

317
00:27:04,840 --> 00:27:08,700
Yan Dan, the mountain was destroyed once because of me.

318
00:27:08,700 --> 00:27:13,840
I can't watch it be destroyed again.

319
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,940
I don't trust you.

320
00:27:26,940 --> 00:27:28,520
Before I give you the immortal spirit,

321
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:32,660
you must call off all the heavenly soldiers from the Night Forgetting River and Yelan Mountain.

322
00:27:32,660 --> 00:27:34,800
And you need to announce to the Three Realms

323
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:37,900
that the mountain and the Heaven Realm will forever stay out of each other's way.

324
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:43,200
Even if the sky falls down or the sun sets in the east, we will never go to war.

325
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,960
Announce it at once.

326
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:50,180
Or else, I'll destroy it myself.

327
00:28:13,660 --> 00:28:18,040
Do you think that you can still escape after the heavenly soldiers have withdrawn?

328
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:25,720
Now that I have no witness here, I can use your lives to try out my Universe Enchantment.

329
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:48,320
- Keep no distance!
- Keep no distance!

330
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:02,580
You... How dare you...

331
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:05,500
This attack is on behalf of Zhi Xi.

332
00:29:05,500 --> 00:29:09,160
I never go back on my word and I will always seek my revenge.

333
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:12,160
Huan Qin, you better calm down.

334
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,780
You can never get rid of the Distance-Keeping Lock.

335
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:20,800
If the spell caster is dead, the Soul Ripping Sword will be stuck forever in your chest.

336
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:26,113
When that happens, I won't be the only one among all the deities who suspect you.

337
00:29:26,113 --> 00:29:28,780
I will kill you today.

338
00:29:28,780 --> 00:29:32,360
Then later I'll slowly torture this lotus spirit!

339
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:37,880
Later? I'm afraid it's too late for you.

340
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:43,120
- Your Supreme Majesty.
 - What is it?

341
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:46,900
Huo De carried the Heavenly Bell to the North Heavenly Gate that connects the Heaven Realm to the Night Forgetting River.

342
00:29:46,900 --> 00:29:48,420
He says that he has something important to report.

343
00:29:48,420 --> 00:29:51,760
I asked him to come to the Night Forgetting River after an hour.

344
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:57,180
At first, I wanted to show him how you abused your power to conduct a personal execution.

345
00:29:57,180 --> 00:30:00,640
But with our current situation, it's even better for him to be here.

346
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:03,440
I want to see just how you're going to explain this.

347
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:06,960
Tell Huo De and the others to meet me at Lingxiao Hall tomorrow.

348
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:09,760
I'll give them an explanation for today's incident.

349
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,700
Huo De already invited all of the deities here.

350
00:30:11,700 --> 00:30:16,140
He said if Your Supreme Majesty won't let them in, they'll barge in to protect you.

351
00:30:16,140 --> 00:30:19,360
Looks like you don't have a choice now.

352
00:30:19,360 --> 00:30:21,380
Ying Yuan and I will take our leave now.

353
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:24,440
If we return to the mountain and find that you have already made the announcement,

354
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:27,300
the heavenly soldiers are gone, and everything is fine,

355
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:31,000
that Distance-Keeping Lock will naturally break on its own.

356
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:35,240
Let's go.

357
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:41,740
Your Supreme Majesty, letting Ying Yuan go is like setting a tiger free.

358
00:30:41,740 --> 00:30:44,320
- If Yan Dan doesn't keep her promise... 
 - Shut up!

359
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:56,440
Why did they all withdraw?

360
00:30:56,440 --> 00:31:00,640
Don't tell me that Ying Yuan and Yan Dan...

361
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:02,480
Impossible.

362
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:07,560
No matter what happens, the two of them definitely won't give up.

363
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:12,580
Since the heavenly soldiers are gone,

364
00:31:12,580 --> 00:31:17,780
you should take all the demons back to the mountain first and get some rest.

365
00:31:17,780 --> 00:31:19,820
I'll try to get some information.

366
00:31:19,820 --> 00:31:22,780
If I don't hear anything from them,

367
00:31:22,780 --> 00:31:27,740
I'll return to the Heaven Realm and fight to my death.

368
00:31:44,860 --> 00:31:46,860
We're back.

369
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:07,820
Before the Universe Enchantment could absorb the immortal spirit, it was stopped by this sword.

370
00:32:07,820 --> 00:32:10,680
All that immortal power was wasted trying to absorb it.

371
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:13,900
A sword through your body will take a toll on your immortal body.

372
00:32:13,900 --> 00:32:15,140
I'll go get the heavenly physician right away.

373
00:32:15,140 --> 00:32:17,220
Huo De is at the North Heavenly Gate now.

374
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:20,840
If you summon the heavenly physician, it'll cause us unnecessary problems.

375
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:23,180
I have half of the Lotus heart.

376
00:32:23,180 --> 00:32:26,300
I can recover quickly from this minor injury.

377
00:32:26,300 --> 00:32:31,100
Right now it is more important to convince the deities to stop them from getting suspicious.

378
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:33,020
Let's head back.

379
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:26,460
My fellow deities. You could've reported to me in court.

380
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:30,200
Is it appropriate for you to gather here at the North Heavenly Gate?

381
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:38,040
Marshal. You are the oldest deity in the Nine Heavens.

382
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:40,740
Why did you bring the Heavenly Bell here without permission?

383
00:33:40,740 --> 00:33:43,340
Do you know what you did wrong?

384
00:33:43,340 --> 00:33:49,000
Putting aside the Heavenly Rules that you've broken, I'm more worried about your health.

385
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:52,550
I don't want you to get hurt.

386
00:33:52,550 --> 00:33:59,630
While we were waiting here, we heard a lot of activity going on at the Night Forgetting River.

387
00:33:59,630 --> 00:34:02,800
Your Majesty, why did you bring our soldiers to the Night Forgetting River at night?

388
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:05,720
The deities and the Demon Clan have always stayed out of each other's way.

389
00:34:05,720 --> 00:34:08,920
Why did Tai You bring an army with him to Yelan Mountain?

390
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:13,770
The traitor, Ying Yuan, colluded with the demon, Yan Dan, to carry out an assassination.

391
00:34:13,770 --> 00:34:17,940
So, I sent a troop after them while Tai You chased after the rest of their accomplices.

392
00:34:17,940 --> 00:34:19,250
Is there anything wrong with that?

393
00:34:19,250 --> 00:34:21,240
Yes!

394
00:34:23,770 --> 00:34:29,080
According to the Heavenly Rules, you must provide a reason before deploying any troops.

395
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:31,740
If the troop has more than ten thousand soldiers you can only deploy them after discussing it

396
00:34:31,740 --> 00:34:34,790
with fellow deities in Lingxiao Hall to show that we are just.

397
00:34:34,790 --> 00:34:37,080
For ten thousand years, no exceptions have ever been made.

398
00:34:37,080 --> 00:34:39,280
Ying Yuan's assassination was too sudden.

399
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,460
We needed to act quickly.

400
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:43,130
How can we stick to the Heavenly Rules?

401
00:34:43,700 --> 00:34:47,150
Your Supreme Majesty once said that the heavenly army cannot be owned

402
00:34:47,150 --> 00:34:50,490
by any of the deities or immortals alone.

403
00:34:50,490 --> 00:34:52,480
None of us can make the decision on our own.

404
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:56,380
Everything that we do is for the peace of the Three Realms.

405
00:34:56,380 --> 00:34:58,420
That's why the rule was made.

406
00:34:58,420 --> 00:35:02,000
Your Supreme Majesty, have you forgotten that?

407
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,480
Marshal. You've overstepped your bounds!

408
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:07,390
Are you saying that as the leader of the Three Realms, His Supreme Majesty

409
00:35:07,390 --> 00:35:09,760
needs your permission to deploy troops?

410
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,740
You have disobeyed His Supreme Majesty's order multiple times.

411
00:35:11,740 --> 00:35:14,020
And you harbored the traitor, Ying Yuan, last night.

412
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:15,500
His Supreme Majesty didn't even hold you accountable for that.

413
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:18,200
But now, you came to ring the Heavenly Bell and are disrespecting His Supreme Majesty.

414
00:35:18,200 --> 00:35:20,280
Where are your manners?!

415
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:21,680
You have no right to talk here!

416
00:35:21,680 --> 00:35:24,620
Huo De. That's too much!

417
00:35:24,620 --> 00:35:25,980
Your Supreme Majesty.

418
00:35:25,980 --> 00:35:29,300
I can only ring the Heavenly Bell if it's something that concerns the Three Realms.

419
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:31,500
Of course, I know that.

420
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:37,680
That's why I had to ring this Heavenly Bell today.

421
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:48,740
Your Supreme Majesty. I am overbearing and have an ill temper.

422
00:35:48,740 --> 00:35:53,960
You have been magnanimous to me because during the War of Genesis,

423
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:58,420
I took a fatal hit for you on the battlefield.

424
00:35:58,420 --> 00:36:01,320
I saved your life.

425
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:04,960
That's why you've always been courteous with me.

426
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:09,140
Back then, you gave me the Letter of Immunity.

427
00:36:09,140 --> 00:36:13,400
And allowed me to talk and act inappropriately all these years.

428
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:15,840
You forgave me for my rudeness and arrogance.

429
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:18,400
I'm grateful to you.

430
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:23,380
All these years I've risked my life to be frank with you because I want to remind you

431
00:36:23,380 --> 00:36:27,720
not to forget about this peace that didn't come easy for the Three Realms.

432
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:30,960
Today, in exchange for your debt to me,

433
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:36,060
I'm begging you to do Emperor Ying Yuan justice.

434
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:45,740
Ever since Emperor Ying Yuan became Emperor Qingli, he has ruled with mercy and virtue.

435
00:36:45,740 --> 00:36:48,200
He has risked his life again and again for the Heaven Realm.

436
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:51,000
It's something that all of us have witnessed.

437
00:36:56,560 --> 00:37:00,500
I, Lu Jing, was a celestial attendant at Yanxu Heavenly Palace for 8,351 years.

438
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:04,240
His Majesty had always done his best to rule and has never been selfish.

439
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:07,320
I'm willing to vouch for him with my life.

440
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:10,080
It's impossible for him to betray us.

441
00:37:11,620 --> 00:37:16,270
I, Zhao Ling, on behalf of the four legions of the heavenly soldiers and 21 elite teams,

442
00:37:16,270 --> 00:37:18,540
beg to tell Your Supreme Majesty this.

443
00:37:18,540 --> 00:37:21,260
We have all been under His Majesty's command.

444
00:37:21,260 --> 00:37:24,340
If His Majesty wanted to betray us, the Heaven Realm would've been destroyed a long time ago.

445
00:37:24,340 --> 00:37:26,660
Please reinvestigate this matter, Your Majesty.

446
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:33,280
Do you think I want to believe that Ying Yuan is a traitor?

447
00:37:33,740 --> 00:37:35,860
I don't want to believe it either!

448
00:37:35,860 --> 00:37:38,820
But we have solid evidence of his assassination.

449
00:37:38,820 --> 00:37:40,870
There's no way to deny it.

450
00:37:41,540 --> 00:37:48,700
Although I'm saddened, miss and cherish Ying Yuan,

451
00:37:48,700 --> 00:37:50,960
I can't go against the Heavenly Rules.

452
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:54,800
I need to punish him accordingly.

453
00:37:56,540 --> 00:37:59,280
The envoy of the Heaven Realm, Tao Ziqi, died a long time ago.

454
00:37:59,280 --> 00:38:02,080
And then she personally identified his crimes in the hall.

455
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:04,700
All of this is too suspicious and there was no conclusive evidence.

456
00:38:04,700 --> 00:38:09,220
But the Alignment of Nine Planets that Emperor Ying Yuan mentioned was true.

457
00:38:09,220 --> 00:38:13,720
When the three Emperors passed away then, I personally saw that alignment in the sky.

458
00:38:13,720 --> 00:38:18,500
This is related to the Divine-Devil War and the death of the three Emperors and hundreds of thousands of heavenly soldiers!

459
00:38:18,500 --> 00:38:20,900
How can you simply conclude the case?

460
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:30,980
Please reinvestigate this case to restore justice to the Three Realms and appease the people!

